    {
        "id": 5,
        "type": "image-with-text",
        "name": null,
        "title": "Catalog & Product implementation catalogs",
        "style": null,
        "align": "right",
        "image": {
            "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/zyMxPBrI.png"
        },
        "content": "<p>Our digital commerce platform provides sophisticated catalog management capabilities making it simple to manage even the most complex B2C and B2B product lists. Using Virto Commerce you can:</p>\n\n<p>Manage digital and physical products. Virto Commerce&#39;s catalog can be configured to handle all your catalog information, or integrated with 3rd party Product Information Management (PIM) or Content Management (CMS) solutions.<br />\nGo Global. Virto Commerce supports multiple catalogs, languages, taxes and storefronts.</p>\n",
        "url1": null,
        "url2": null
    },
    {
        "id": 6,
        "type": "image-with-text",
        "name": null,
        "title": "Pricing",
        "style": "dark",
        "align": "left",
        "image": {
            "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/pricing.png"
        },
        "content": "<p>B2B companies order large volumes, so naturally they negotiate different pricing with different buyers. B2B-specific software needs to be able to reflect customer relationships and/or specific order conditions like pricing, special offers, and special conditions for shipping and delivery.</p>\n\n<p>Virto Commerce can support all your B2B pricing needs. Prices can be personalized in real-time based on audience, campaign, purchase history, geo-location, contracts and other customer-based scenarios.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Personalized pricing</li>\n\t<li>Price lists &middot; B2B pricing</li>\n\t<li>Tiered pricing</li>\n\t<li>Custom currencies (bitcoin, points)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"#\">Learn More about our Pricing Functionality</a></p>\n",
        "url1": null,
        "url2": null
    },
    {
        "id": 7,
        "type": "image-with-text",
        "name": null,
        "title": "Multy Tenant",
        "style": null,
        "align": "right",
        "image": {
            "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/Multi-tenant_1.png"
        },
        "content": "<p>B2B vendors need to deal with the challenge of managing multiple vendors in a catalog while allowing customers to view the updated catalog in real time. Their solution needs to support multi-vendor catalogs, where all data - about all available products- by every vendor you work with - is stored in one place and can be easily accessed, updated and shared with all parties involved. Virto Commerce enables you to create complex rule structures, allow vendors to accept orders and customize the look and feel of their storefront.</p>\n\n<p class=\"section__descr--medium\"><strong>Virto&#39;s software allows you to:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Create organizations</li>\n\t<li>Vendor store themes and templates</li>\n\t<li>Relate orders to specific vendor/store</li>\n\t<li>Control vendor permissions</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "url1": null,
        "url2": null
    },
    {
        "id": 8,
        "type": "image-with-text",
        "name": "API based",
        "title": "Api based",
        "style": "dark",
        "align": "left",
        "image": {
            "url": "http://localhost/admin/assets/blogs/api-based.png"
        },
        "content": "<p>Virto Commerce&#39;s modular architecture supports REST based APIs. These APIs allow you integrate other business systems and frontend technologies, such as customer profile data or a chat bot, into your Virto Commerce solution.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Modular architecture to customize your solution</li>\n\t<li>Real-time exchange of data</li>\n\t<li>Secure: REST Oauth and token based authentication ensures your data will never be breeched</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"#\">Explore our API</a></p>\n",
        "url1": null,
        "url2": null
    },
    {
        "id": 9,
        "type": "image-with-text",
        "name": null,
        "title": "Order Management",
        "style": null,
        "align": "right",
        "image": {
            "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/Order_management_1.png"
        },
        "content": "<p>Virto Commerce provides industry leading order management functionality. It can be integrated into complex enterprise workflows -- including many leading ERP and fulfillment systems.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Customer order history</li>\n\t<li>Split shipments</li>\n\t<li>Split payments</li>\n\t<li>Punchout support</li>\n\t<li>Quotes &amp; purchase orders</li>\n\t<li>Subscription management</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "url1": null,
        "url2": null
    },
    {
        "id": 10,
        "type": "image-with-text",
        "name": null,
        "title": "Open Source",
        "style": "dark",
        "align": "left",
        "image": {
            "url": "http://localhost/admin/assets/blogs/open-source.png"
        },
        "content": "<p>Virto Commerce is Open Source. Virto Commerce&#39;s platform allows you limitless access to modify the platform&#39;s code, giving your team endless creative freedom to configure your B2B website to meet your exact specifications.</p>\n\n<p class=\"section__descr--medium\">Other benefits that come along with leveraging the power of an open source solution:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Empower highly customized B2B store fronts by downloading the code and customize the platform yourself.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"#\">Join the Virto Commerce community of developers</a></p>\n",
        "url1": null,
        "url2": null
    },
